{"title":"哈尔滨记事（二首）","authors":["李冰牧"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":4,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈尔滨记事（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李冰牧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排队，买大面包"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈尔滨谚语："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大面包象锅盖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切一片吧，这大面包样子憨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咬一口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酸中透着艮，艮中裹着甜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片面包，一杯白水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是妻子的早点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是儿子的午餐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是习惯，非为省钱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在是怕时间的金子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随淘米水流走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难请的诗神给炒勺声赶散"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排队去买吧，大面包"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈尔滨人对它有特殊的情感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"串烤羊肉，从新疆来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"健美的身躯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打足了笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一个大塑料娃娃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸蛋鼓溜溜油汪汪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一顶维吾尔族的小花帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美得要往空中飘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"串烤羊肉，从新疆来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咝咝唱，飘着馋人的香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到美丽的松花江边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到迷人的太阳岛上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈尔滨人慷慨地笑了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"串烤羊肉，来自雪山天池"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自沙漠红柳丛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自农场大路的钻天杨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自哈密的葡萄干的故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正巧，博物馆展览"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄胄的小毛驴叫得好响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"串烤羊肉，来自新疆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从祖国的大西北"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到祖国的大东北"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路并不遥远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他却走了三十年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比古代的旅人还慢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，乘着快车来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路过北京，用不了几天"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}